Net::BEEP::Lite::TLSProfile version 0.01
==========================

Net::BEEP::Lite::TLSProfile is (as it's name implies) a TLS profile
implementation for Net::BEEP::Lite.

There is an example client and server in the test directory
(test_tls_echo_client.pl and test_tls_echo_server.pl) that can be used
as a starting point, in addition to the built-in POD documentation.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  IO::Socket::SSL
  XML::LibXML

